quran[8]{c,v,t}:
  22,16,aur isi terhan hum ne is quran ko utaara hai ( jis ki tamam ) baatein khuli hui ( hain ) aur yeh ( yaad rakho ) ke khuda jis ko chahta hai Hadayat deta hai
  22,17,jo log momin ( yani musalman ) hain aur jo yahodi hain aur sitara parast aur isaai aur majoosi aur mushriq. khuda un ( sab ) mein qayamat ke din faisla kardey ga. be shak khuda har cheez se bakhabar hai
  22,18,kiya tum ne nahi dekha ke jo ( makhlooq ) asmano mein hai aur jo zameen mein hai aur Sooraj aur chaand setaaray aur pahar aur darakht aur chaar paye aur bohat se ensaan khuda ko sajda karte hain. aur bohat se aisay hain jin par azaab saabit hochuka hai. aur jis shakhs ko khuda zaleel kere is ko izzat dainay wala nahi. be shak khuda jo chahta hai karta hai
  22,19,yeh do ( fareeq ) aik dosray ke dushman apne perwar-digaar ( ke baray ) mein jhagarte hain. to kafir hain un ke liye aag ke kapray qata kiye jayen ge ( aur ) un ke suron par jalta howa pani dala jaye ga
  22,20,is se un ke pait ke andar ki cheezein aur khalin Gul jayen gi
  22,21,aur un ( ke maarny thoknay ) ke liye lohay ke hathoray hon ge
  22,22,jab woh chahain ge ke is ranj ( wa takleef ) ki wajah se dozakh se nikal jayen to phir isi mein lota diye jayen ge. aur ( kaha jaye ga ke ) julne ke azaab ka maza chahkte raho
  22,23,jo log imaan laaye aur amal naik karte rahay khuda un ko bahishtoon mein daakhil kere ga jin ke taley nehrain beh rahen hain. wahan un ko sonay ke kangon pahnaye jayen ge aur moti. aur wahan un ka libaas reshmi hoga
